overview: The user's intent was to add a 'Surprise me' button to the application
  that would navigate to a random blog post. The assistant identified the
   component as the appropriate location for this button. The
  initial approach involved using Next.js's  for navigation, but this
  led to a runtime error related to module instantiation. To resolve this, the
  navigation method was changed to , which successfully
  allowed the button to redirect to a random post. The button was styled using
  the existing  component with a secondary variant and positioned at the
  top right of the posts list.
